body: i really wish we didn’t get steve&peggy dance scene in endgame. old steve didn’t want to talk with sam about his life, he wanted to keep it to himself and that’s great. this and that shot with steve’s hand with wedding ring would be enough. we could add a story we like. it wouldn’t have to mean that steve married peggy, it also could be someone else *cough*tony
